  <body>
    <section name="Property types">
      <p>
        EasyConf supports typed access to the configuration properties of a component.
        The current supported types are (in alphabetic order):
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>BigDecimal</li>
        <li>BigInteger</li>
        <li>Boolean</li>
        <li>Byte</li>
        <li>Class: useful for implementing plugins</li>
        <li>ClassArray: useful for implementing plugin chains</li>
        <li>Double</li>
        <li>Float</li>
        <li>Integer</li>
        <li>List</li>
        <li>Long</li>
        <li>Short</li>
        <li>String: supports usage of variables</li>
        <li>StringArray: supports usage of variables</li>
      </ul>
      </section>
    </body>
  </document>